on\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From British Path\\u00e9, Emil Z\\u00e1topek wins the marathon at the Helsinki Olympic Games, his first ever time running that distance Z\\u00e1topek became a great athlete despite enduring food shortages linked to World War II and the Cold War.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Path\\u00e9_News\", \"score\": 0.8835314487922844, \"rank\": 0.13182025058897365, \"text\": \"British Path\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Path\\u00e9_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Path\\u00e9_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Z\\u00e1topek_(film)\", \"score\": 0.9733031809810366, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Z\\u00e1topek\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Z\\u00e1topek_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Z\\u00e1topek_(film)\"}, {\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Z\\u00e1topek_(film)\", \"score\": 0.9733031809810366, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Z\\u00e1topek\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Z\\u00e1topek_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Z\\u00e1topek_(film)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"the Helsinki Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"his first ever time\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2314}, {\"ngram\": \"that distance\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"a great athlete\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"food shortages\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"World War II\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"the Cold War\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That does not mean his food choices were not a little strange at times.\", \"