atoes\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then there were pancakes and oatmeal, lots of fruit, topped off with French vanilla coffee.\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pancakes\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"fruit\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3481}, {\"ngram\": \"French vanilla coffee\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like many athletes involved in endurance exercise, Lochte frequently employed the practice ofcarb-loading.\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3574, \"end\": 3580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lochte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance exercise\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"the practice ofcarb-loading\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This involves consuming a carbohydrate-rich diet to increase the amount of stored energy as glycogen in your muscles.\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a carbohydrate-rich diet\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3678}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"stored energy\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3718}, {\"ngram\": \"glycogen\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"your muscles\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Lochte, his carb-loading involved a week of spaghetti, fettuccine Alfredo in particular.\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3752, \"end\": 3758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lochte\